    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv Thanks for the options however `attributeName` was not accessible nor available in my custom template. I even dropped all available variables with function instead of a string template.\r\n\r\nThe reason for the unique name was due to how the toggles were originally designed. Wrapping them does ruin the UI of it (tho that can be easily fixed by updating the CSS).\r\n\r\nAlso thanks for the tip on `refinementList`, I'll take a look!",
